<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="78" type="specimens examined">
<paragraph pageId="11" pageNumber="78">Specimens examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="11" pageNumber="78">Holotype, male. CHINA. Hubei province, Shennongjia, Dalongtan, sweep-net, 20.V.2012, Kai Shi [SM01662].</paragraph>
